WEBVTT

00:01.074 --> 00:02.589
This is where I saved you
from saved you from ***.

00:02.613 --> 00:04.553
We'll be there
in a couple hours.

00:04.577 --> 00:07.170
Previously on
<i>Falling Skies...</i>

00:07.840 --> 00:10.158
This sanctuary here turned out
too good to be true.

00:10.404 --> 00:11.887
If she's meeting
with the enemy

00:11.911 --> 00:13.374
and she's not telling us about it.

00:13.451 --> 00:15.211
Let's just give her
the benefit of the doubt.

00:15.218 --> 00:15.907
She's earned that.

00:15.931 --> 00:16.434
Okay.

00:16.458 --> 00:17.458
But I'm bringing my guns.

00:17.771 --> 00:19.158
You lied to me, Lexi.

00:19.739 --> 00:21.202
What are your plans
for my daughter?

00:21.502 --> 00:23.728
Soon the transformation
will begin.

00:24.968 --> 00:25.968
Someone let the monk go.

00:26.705 --> 00:27.983
Did you do this?

