01:06.629 --> 01:08.663
It's Hal.

01:08.665 --> 01:10.465
Shh.

01:19.342 --> 01:21.109
Where were you?

01:27.050 --> 01:28.783
Ben.

01:28.785 --> 01:29.785
Ben?

01:32.354 --> 01:33.688
I'm -- I'm up.
Come in.

01:34.690 --> 01:36.257
How are you feeling?

01:36.259 --> 01:37.692
I wanted
to let you sleep,

01:37.694 --> 01:40.395
but Anne convinced me
I should get you.

01:40.397 --> 01:41.996
I'm fine.
What's wrong?

01:41.998 --> 01:44.132
The Overlord
she was interrogating escaped.

01:44.134 --> 01:46.200
What? No, Anthony was
guarding him. He was chained.

01:46.202 --> 01:47.335
I think
Lexi let him go.

01:47.337 --> 01:49.437
No.
Lexi was deathly sick.

01:49.439 --> 01:51.439
Well,
we got to get him back.

01:51.441 --> 01:53.608
We're doing
a full perimeter sweep.

01:53.610 --> 01:55.343
We need you.

02:00.482 --> 02:02.116
What's wrong?

02:02.118 --> 02:04.652
They're looking for him.
Should I do something?

02:04.654 --> 02:06.521
They won't find him.

02:06.523 --> 02:08.423
They're so afraid of him.

02:08.425 --> 02:10.358
I think
they're afraid of <i>me.</i>

02:10.360 --> 02:12.226
It doesn't matter
what they think.

02:12.228 --> 02:14.328
Maggie's with them.

02:14.330 --> 02:16.597
She used to believe in me,
but now...

02:16.599 --> 02:18.299
Everything's changing.

02:18.301 --> 02:21.102
<i>I</i> haven't changed.
I never will.

02:21.104 --> 02:23.271
Humans talk so much
about change,

02:23.273 --> 02:24.739
but they're afraid of it.

02:24.741 --> 02:26.307
Why?

02:26.309 --> 02:28.176
We're weak,
afraid of the unknown.

02:28.178 --> 02:29.811
Don't be afraid.

02:29.813 --> 02:31.612
My father is returning.

02:31.614 --> 02:33.214
I need to be ready.

02:33.216 --> 02:35.516
Tom's coming here?

02:39.121 --> 02:40.354
I'd like to be alone.

02:58.349 --> 03:02.349
